1. Preamble & Authorship

This software, "Freetopify" (the "Software"), is an original creative work conceived, designed, and developed by Aditya Singh (operating under the handle flexcreates). The Software was created as a personal project for self-hosting and managing personal music libraries.

Development Methodology:
While the Software's architecture, user experience flows, and problem-solving approaches are the original intellectual property of Aditya Singh, portions of the source code were generated or refined through the use of artificial intelligence coding assistants. AI tools served solely as implementation assistants—similar to advanced code editors or autocomplete systems—while all creative direction, design decisions, feature specifications, and debugging strategies were created and directed by the author.

AI tools are agents, not authors. The use of AI for code generation does not transfer ownership or diminish the author's intellectual property rights in any way.

